22
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:03,430
Oh, we're not suspicious.
We just had a question.

23
00:01:03,496 --> 00:01:04,397
Okay.

24
00:01:04,464 --> 00:01:07,434
Do you know a building called
Angel Forest Tower?

25
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:08,668
Sure.

26
00:01:09,602 --> 00:01:12,372
-Cross here, turn right…
-So it is famous.

27
00:01:13,940 --> 00:01:15,108
Well, I live there.

28
00:01:15,175 --> 00:01:18,044
<i>I had her quite young. She's already 20.</i>

29
00:01:18,111 --> 00:01:21,815
I want my daughter to experience love.

30
00:01:22,549 --> 00:01:26,052
There are parts of you that can only grow
through romance.

31
00:01:26,119 --> 00:01:30,323
Most of all, don't you think it's sad to
not know the feeling of being in love

32
00:01:30,390 --> 00:01:32,358
after being born in this world?

33
00:01:32,425 --> 00:01:33,259
<i>THE SOUND OF DREAMS</i>

34
00:01:33,326 --> 00:01:35,095
You want and pursue someone,

35
00:01:35,161 --> 00:01:36,863
you get hurt, you hurt them,

36
00:01:36,930 --> 00:01:38,498
and you learn what it is to be human.

37
00:01:39,699 --> 00:01:41,434
Those without that experience are weak.

38
00:01:44,270 --> 00:01:46,406
Are you listening, Ms. Matsuyama?

39
00:01:49,275 --> 00:01:51,978
Sorry, don't shoot from below.

40
00:01:52,045 --> 00:01:54,080
The upper right is my best angle.

41
00:01:54,147 --> 00:01:55,014
Yes, ma'am.

42
00:01:57,884 --> 00:01:59,052
<i>You don't know her?</i>

43
00:01:59,119 --> 00:02:01,788
Aoi Minase, the queen of romance novels.

44
00:02:02,755 --> 00:02:04,757
I guess kids these days don't know her.

45
00:02:04,824 --> 00:02:09,262
Like the <i>Sound of Dreams</i> or
<i>Seeing You Tomorrow.</i>

46
00:02:09,329 --> 00:02:11,731
It took the world by storm back then.

47
00:02:12,332 --> 00:02:13,399
How about now?

48
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,769
-Well, it's hard to say…
-Past its prime?

49
00:02:17,504 --> 00:02:18,872
You're a straight talker!

50
00:02:19,672 --> 00:02:20,974
You said turn right here…

51
