52
00:02:22,775 --> 00:02:25,678
I didn't think I'd be concerned
about this.

53
00:02:25,745 --> 00:02:28,581
Ever since my daughter was young,
my concern was

54
00:02:28,648 --> 00:02:30,884
what if she gets caught up
with the wrong guy?

55
00:02:30,950 --> 00:02:34,687
But there hasn't been a single guy
pursuing her.

56
00:02:34,754 --> 00:02:37,190
