57
00:02:37,257 --> 00:02:39,325
What if she never gets a boyfriend, and…

58
00:02:39,392 --> 00:02:41,394
Even though her mother's a
master of romance?

59
00:02:41,461 --> 00:02:42,562
A master? Me?

60
00:02:42,629 --> 00:02:46,132
You've written so many romance novels.

61
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:48,101
