77
00:03:25,772 --> 00:03:28,808
I do, but that's an apology gift.

78
00:03:29,976 --> 00:03:33,413
So observant… Don't worry about me.
Please continue your interview.

79
00:03:34,147 --> 00:03:35,248
We'll talk later.

80
