That was otterly weird. Get otter here!

95
00:04:18,758 --> 00:04:20,693
THIS IS A SMALL-CLAWED OTTER!

96
00:04:23,363 --> 00:04:25,465
Oh? You're the girl from earlier.

97
00:04:25,531 --> 00:04:27,033
