108
00:05:00,566 --> 00:05:01,501
SUZURAN SHOPPING DISTRICT

109
00:05:01,567 --> 00:05:03,770
<i>The Suzuran Shopping District is</i>

110
00:05:03,836 --> 00:05:05,605
<i>a historic site that has been thriving</i>

111
