<i>for over 300 years</i>
<i>as a temple town since the Edo period.</i>

112
00:05:09,275 --> 00:05:11,577
<i>In the center of</i>
<i>Suzuran Shopping District,</i>

113
00:05:11,644 --> 00:05:13,012
<i>right in the middle of Tokyo,</i>

114
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:15,448
<i>is the bathhouse, Suzuran Hot Springs.</i>

115
00:05:15,515 --> 00:05:17,617
<i>Next to that is the historical</i>
<i>taiyaki shop,</i>

116
00:05:17,684 --> 00:05:20,186
<i>Odaya. Gon-chan is the fourth generation</i>
<i>shop owner.</i>

117
00:05:22,622 --> 00:05:23,656
<i>This is Gon-chan.</i>

118
00:05:24,991 --> 00:05:25,958
How is it?

119
00:05:28,761 --> 00:05:30,897
Another bite! Eat another bite!

120
00:05:30,963 --> 00:05:33,666
<i>This is Gon-chan's dad, Shunichiro.</i>

121
00:05:33,733 --> 00:05:35,768
-Excuse me?
-Yes, sir!

122
00:05:35,835 --> 00:05:38,371
<i>Odaya, struggling from the</i>
<i>recent tapioca boom,</i>

123
00:05:38,438 --> 00:05:40,707
