124
00:05:40,773 --> 00:05:44,043
<i>That was the sanmayaki,</i>
<i>instead of the taiyaki.</i>

125
00:05:44,110 --> 00:05:47,613
Welcome, everyone!
We have some delicious taiyaki!

126
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,716
We have whole beans, crushed beans,

127
00:05:49,782 --> 00:05:52,618
Indian beans, alien beans… Just kidding!

128
00:05:52,685 --> 00:05:53,953
We have everything!

129
00:05:55,688 --> 00:05:57,890
-Right?
-I know!

130
00:05:57,957 --> 00:06:00,560
