131
00:06:00,626 --> 00:06:02,695
Our bean paste is really good!

132
00:06:02,762 --> 00:06:06,032
Yes, of course it's good,
but there's just too much.

133
00:06:06,899 --> 00:06:07,734
What?

134
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,869
<i>That was a big shock to Gon-chan.</i>

135
00:06:10,436 --> 00:06:14,006
<i>In his life, he never doubted the</i>
<i>universal good of stuffing taiyaki</i>

136
00:06:14,073 --> 00:06:16,476
<i>with as much bean paste as possible,</i>
<i>to the tail.</i>

137
00:06:18,010 --> 00:06:21,614
<i>With this experience, he invented</i>
<i>the sanmayaki, with less bean paste.</i>

138
00:06:23,983 --> 00:06:26,419
So this is the sanmayaki?

139
00:06:26,486 --> 00:06:28,187
I'm not a fan of too much bean paste.

140
00:06:28,254 --> 00:06:30,623
That's why Odaya made this for me.

141
00:06:30,690 --> 00:06:33,826
-She's lying.
-If there's only a little bit of paste,

142
00:06:33,893 --> 00:06:35,995
