143
00:06:36,662 --> 00:06:40,199
So they're testing a new recipe
with white bean paste. Right, Sora?

144
00:06:40,266 --> 00:06:41,100
Roger that.

145
00:06:41,167 --> 00:06:42,602
That's not how you use that word.

146
00:06:43,336 --> 00:06:44,604
Can I eat some, too?

147
00:06:45,438 --> 00:06:46,272
Roger that.

148
00:06:51,244 --> 00:06:54,614
I'm sorry this is more bean paste, but…
Here you are.

149
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,983
Hey, Sora's right there!

150
00:06:57,049 --> 00:06:59,118
Tatsuya's bean jelly,
kneaded with apologies.

151
00:06:59,185 --> 00:07:01,354
The weight of the jelly represents
the guilt.

152
00:07:01,421 --> 00:07:04,257
Red bean paste,
stewed and simmered apologies.

153
