157
00:07:23,209 --> 00:07:25,745
Oh, sorry! I need to take this.

158
00:07:26,479 --> 00:07:27,914
Hey, wassup?

159
00:07:28,614 --> 00:07:31,751
You're in Nishiazabu? Sure.
Right now? Yeah, sure.

160
00:07:33,019 --> 00:07:36,789
Yes. Ask them to open early.
You're a VIP, they'd do that!

161
00:07:36,856 --> 00:07:38,591
And who are you?

162
00:07:39,625 --> 00:07:42,862
Everything is so chaotic, I haven't
had the chance to introduce…

163
00:07:42,929 --> 00:07:45,298
