164
00:07:45,364 --> 00:07:48,534
Alright, got it!
I'll just deal with this quickly.

165
00:07:49,068 --> 00:07:50,970
I'll be right over. Okay!

166
00:07:52,972 --> 00:07:55,308
Oh, sorry about that.

167
00:07:55,374 --> 00:07:57,443
Apologies, apologies.

168
00:07:57,510 --> 00:07:59,745
You know, you might call me

169
00:07:59,812 --> 00:08:01,581
a little outdated, but…

170
00:08:02,815 --> 00:08:04,750
Ms. Aoi. I'm so sorry about this.

171
00:08:04,817 --> 00:08:07,620
Wait, don't say it! Sora's here!

172
00:08:07,687 --> 00:08:09,055
Hey, don't you have work?

173
00:08:09,121 --> 00:08:10,156
After I eat this.

174
00:08:10,223 --> 00:08:14,126
Your series at Raphael
will end next month.

175
00:08:14,193 --> 00:08:15,261
Canceled.

176
00:08:17,997 --> 00:08:19,499
No!

177
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:21,267
We're so sorry.

178
00:08:23,669 --> 00:08:27,773
I guess I'm too out of touch
for this line of work…

179
00:08:28,407 --> 00:08:29,609
Huh?

180
00:08:29,675 --> 00:08:32,211
The series at Raphael is
<i>Umbilical Cord,</i> right?

181
00:08:32,278 --> 00:08:35,581
You said we'd release season two,
serialize it, and make a movie…

182
00:08:37,617 --> 00:08:40,386
See! It says Season One right here!

183
00:08:40,453 --> 00:08:42,388
Season One is the end.

184
00:08:42,455 --> 00:08:43,956
What the hell?

185
00:08:44,023 --> 00:08:46,993
Well… This book…

186
00:08:47,059 --> 00:08:50,396
