187
00:08:50,463 --> 00:08:51,564
Not at all.

188
00:08:51,631 --> 00:08:53,366
Soften it.

189
00:08:53,432 --> 00:08:56,402
Soften the blow! You're too frank!

190
00:08:56,469 --> 00:08:59,038
We need a little frankness at times,
don't you think?

191
00:08:59,105 --> 00:09:02,275
This proves Aoi Minase is
a romance writer after all.

192
00:09:02,341 --> 00:09:03,609
Mystery wasn't your thing.

193
