Truly, no one.

197
00:09:18,891 --> 00:09:19,959
So who will it be?

198
00:09:20,626 --> 00:09:21,527
Huh?

199
00:09:21,594 --> 00:09:23,896
Who's going to take over
my spot at Raphael?

200
00:09:25,965 --> 00:09:29,435
We found someone really good!

201
00:09:29,502 --> 00:09:30,469
Who?

202
00:09:30,536 --> 00:09:32,939
The handsome TV star, Tomoro Nakagawa.

203
00:09:33,005 --> 00:09:35,141
-You know him too, right, Sora?
-No.

204
00:09:35,207 --> 00:09:37,677
She's an otaku. Only interested in 2D men.
