-He's drinking at a bar.

213
00:09:55,661 --> 00:09:57,196
-Wait!
-It sure is nice to be young.

214
00:09:57,263 --> 00:09:59,565
"Wait, will you?" That's a Kimutaku quote.

215
00:09:59,632 --> 00:10:00,866
Wait.

216
00:10:00,933 --> 00:10:03,469
He's an actor, right? An actor!
This Nakagawa man.

217
00:10:03,536 --> 00:10:06,672
