240
00:11:06,999 --> 00:11:11,971
Yes. No matter how hard I work,
a woman would never be promoted.

241
00:11:12,038 --> 00:11:16,108
Instead of being bossed around
by stupid young men,

242
00:11:16,175 --> 00:11:18,978
