00:50:56,186 --> 00:50:59,156
HOW WILL THEIR ROMANCE TURN OUT?

867
00:51:06,430 --> 00:51:08,298
I'm going to go find love right now!

868
00:51:08,365 --> 00:51:10,033
-She's on a date!
-What?

869
00:51:10,100 --> 00:51:11,535
So you're an otaku too?

870
00:51:11,601 --> 00:51:13,603
<i>It's a secret that I'm an otaku.</i>

871
00:51:13,670 --> 00:51:15,172
Want to go together?

872
00:51:15,238 --> 00:51:18,275
-What's going on?
<i>-Maybe no one sees me as a woman anymore.</i>

873
00:51:18,341 --> 00:51:20,877
-Ms. Aoi?
<i>-Love might be a battle.</i>

